commit.message: refs #4879 allow persistent connections to disable the idle disconnect while in progress
refs #4879 implemented a reconnect on HTTP send/receive operations if already connected and an immediate disconnect occurs
fixed non-scu builds
refs #4878 added a default idle disconnect to HTTP connections
fixed a bug setting record child entries in type entries
allow implied options to be set with qdp
fixed gmail attachment polling
improved REST app/action
fixes to RestClientDataProvider app actions
refs #4008 fixed Discord WS gateway reconnect handling when a reconnection must be made before the READY message arrives
refs #4008 fixed Discord author data in message data type
increased max thread limit to 8192
added '*byte' types, renamed unsigned byte types to '*ubyte', added tests for the rgbcolor type
added min and max options for the data provider int type, added unsigned byte types + an rgbcolor type
added ModuleManager::issueRuntimeCmd()
refs #4876 fixed base type value
refs #4876 allow types to return simple type info for accept and returns compatibility (#4877)
